<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1183 gu 
<lb n="2"/>nēṁṭi durmu khasaṁvatsara caitraba 6 śa 
<lb n="3"/>nāṁṭi viṣuvusaṁkrāntinimittamu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na śrītripurāṁtakadēvaraku Iṁdulū 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ri gaṇapaya koḍuku gannaya Akhaṁḍadīpā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>na kiccinamōdālu 25 vīniṁ jēkoni gu 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tripura nityatavveṁḍu neyi naḍapaṁga <unclear>lavāṁḍu</unclear> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

<p><hi rend="italic">Note.</hi>— durmukha seems to be An Error for durmati• </p>

